|CKBBrew Element: Weather, Now Available in Glass|000

Syntax: brewelement <fire|ice|lightning>
Alias:  elementpotion

At Rank 3, Volatility 2, and Alchemy 75, prepare one owner-bound flask of
bottled fire, ice, or lightning. Only one elemental flask may be carried at a
time. It lasts two hours and delivers the advertised weather when thrown.

Use 'throw <element> flask at <target>'. While fighting, omit 'at <target>'
to throw it at your current foe. Each successful throw consumes the flask,
engages combat, and kicks some of the blast back onto you. Drinking one is
technically possible and medically discouraging.
